Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP「LOVE or HATE?」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば髪をちょっとなびかせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聴こえる声{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:25.92,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　何と言われても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}足は止めませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:32.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}飛ぶ鳥落とす勢い　ニュース
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:35.36,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}明日には忘れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:39.34,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}昨日よりも今日がいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:42.29,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}思い込み　大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:45.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}リズムに合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:49.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}揺れていたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}外野がうるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.13,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ノイズ・キャンセリング
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば指をちょっとなぞらせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.76,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君のチョイス{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　頬を赤くして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}唾を吐きかけ{\fsp4}る{\fsp0}Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}趣味の違い　安心の相違が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.60,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君を戸惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}私の道　形作るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:23.48,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}これだけ　Just LOVE or HATE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是撩一下頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聽到的會是喜歡還是討厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:25.92,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隨便吧 無論別人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}反正不會停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:32.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}新聞的傳播勢不可擋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:35.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}到了明天就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:39.34,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以今天比昨天好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:42.29,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}精神勝利大法好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:45.84,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}本想跟著節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:49.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}搖擺搖擺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.84,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但外面也太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.13,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}噪音·消除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是用手指轉個圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.76,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你的選擇是喜歡還是討厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隨便吧 憋紅了臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.84,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}準備唾棄的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}興趣的不同 信仰的不一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.60,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}讓你感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但決定我前行方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:23.48,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}僅僅是喜歡還是討厭
